summary: My study started at Radius College, Breda. Here I graduated as laboratory technician.  After this study I chose to continue my studies at Avans Hogeschool, Breda. This study in chemical product innovation made me more specialized in organic and polymer chemistry. In between my study years I worked at Makro Breda as costumer assistant.
